{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_01_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ばぁっ！",
      "startTime": 1.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ？\n誰だっ！？",
      "startTime": 2.7226984043916067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ぷくく……\nうわぁ、だって",
      "startTime": 5.439365076356463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、え？\nな……なんだ？　奥山さん？",
      "startTime": 9.339365076356463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "こんにちはっ{user}さん！\nビックリさせてごめんなさい。えへへ",
      "startTime": 15.572698409689801,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "実はさっき窓から見えたんです。スタジオに\n入ってきたから待ち伏せして驚かせようかな～と思って",
      "startTime": 21.495269304845063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに驚くなんて\n{user}さんもまだまだですね～",
      "startTime": 27.9286026381784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、今日はスタジオになんのご用ですか？",
      "startTime": 31.061935971511737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "これからウチのグループのレッスン時間なんです\n……ん？　その紙袋は……？",
      "startTime": 37.99193586342864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、これですか？\nふっふっふ、なんだと思います？",
      "startTime": 42.85860253009529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "正解は～……じゃーん！！\n芋煮缶でした～！！",
      "startTime": 49.558602530095285,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_takeout-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1866.6666666666601,
          "startTime": 48.25860253009528
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "芋煮缶？\nえ？　そんなものあるんですか？",
      "startTime": 53.59193586342862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "もー、反応薄いですよ\nもっと驚いてくれてもいいんですからね？",
      "startTime": 59.12526919676196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "実はこれ、私の地元の限定商品なんですよね\n私、山形出身なんです",
      "startTime": 66.09193586342863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（だから時々方言が出るんだな）",
      "startTime": 68.62220802936288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あれ？　でも奥山さんは中学生ですよね\nまさか実家から通ってる訳じゃ……",
      "startTime": 76.02220802936287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "実家通いですよ？",
      "startTime": 78.82220802936287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "スタジオでレッスンがある日や\nライブのある日は、実家から通ってます",
      "startTime": 82.22930553588598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンやライブのたびに\n山形と東京を往復してるんですか……大変ですね",
      "startTime": 86.86263886921932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、よく言われますけど、そうでもないですよ？\n片道三時間もあれば着きますから",
      "startTime": 96.62930553588598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "移動時間だって、ステージの映像を見たり曲を聴いて\nおさらいしてたら、あっという間です",
      "startTime": 102.92930553588596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "それに、実家に帰ったら\nお兄ちゃんと東京のお話一杯出来ますし",
      "startTime": 107.02930553588595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "東京に来れば瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんに会えますし\n疲れなんて吹っ飛んじゃいますから！",
      "startTime": 113.66609665990104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "一石二鳥です！",
      "startTime": 115.96609665990104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（きっと大変なのに、微塵も疲れを感じさせない笑顔だ）\n（プロアイドルの凄みを感じるな）",
      "startTime": 122.39943004091808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "たまーにレッスンやステージが\n遅くなったりすることがあるんですけど",
      "startTime": 126.7660967075848,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr019.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時は、瑠依ちゃんと優ちゃんのマンションに\nお泊りさせてもらってますし！",
      "startTime": 132.28508061607909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "へえ……天動さんと鈴村さんは\n同じマンションに住んでるんですか？",
      "startTime": 137.8517472827458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr020.m4a",
      "text": "はい、部屋もお隣同士なんですよ\n三人で一緒にご飯食べたりして凄く楽しいんです！",
      "startTime": 143.28508061607923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr021.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、そうだ！\n良かったら芋煮缶、食べて下さい",
      "startTime": 148.85174728274595,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　もらえるならありがたくいただきますけど……\n本当にいいんですか？",
      "startTime": 155.8517472827459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr022.m4a",
      "text": "遠慮しないで下さい\nだってこれ、まだまだ沢山ありますから",
      "startTime": 159.38508061607908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr023.m4a",
      "text": "スタジオの控え室に、あと十ダースありますよ！",
      "startTime": 162.31841394941245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr024.m4a",
      "text": "芋煮って、あんなに美味しいのに、食べられてるのは\n東北だけなんですよね……東京に来てびっくりしました",
      "startTime": 169.3235385978247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr025.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私の地元の味を知ってもらいたくて\n箱買いしちゃいました。えへへ",
      "startTime": 176.9902052644913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr026.m4a",
      "text": "良かったら星見プロのみなさんにも\nおすそ分けしますから、持って帰って下さい",
      "startTime": 182.35687193115797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それなら遠慮せず、いただきますね。そういえばこの間\n奥山さんが食べていたおしるこ、美味しかったですよ",
      "startTime": 189.5902052644913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-smr027.m4a",
      "text": "……！\nはぁー……良かったです",
      "startTime": 194.65687193115787,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
